<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Us - StreamAPI</title>
    <style>
        /* Email-specific styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #f8f9fa;
            background-color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .email-logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .email-body {
            background-color: #374151;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #4b5563;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .message-details {
            background-color: #2d3748;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="email-logo">
                <span style="color: #10b981;">&#9658;</span> StreamAPI
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Thanks for Getting in Touch!</h1>
            
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for contacting StreamAPI. We have received your message and our team will review it shortly. We typically respond to inquiries within 24-48 hours.</p>
            
            <div class="message-details">
                <h3>Your Message Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= subject %></p>
                <p><strong>Message:</strong><br><%= message %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore our platform for the latest movies and TV shows.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= siteUrl %>" class="button">Visit StreamAPI</a>
            </div>
            
            <hr>
            
            <p>If you have any other questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out again.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The StreamAPI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Github</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Discord</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> StreamAPI. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Created by <a href="https://github.com/BotCoder254" style="color: #10b981;">@BotCoder254</a></p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px;">
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 